<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.3.8">
<l>paḷḷiyi lōti vantataṉ ciṟuvaṉ vāyilō rāyira nāma</l>
<l>moḷḷiya vākip pōtavāṅ kataṉuk koṉṟumōr poṟuppila ṉāki</l>
<l>piḷḷaiyaic cīṟi vekuṇṭutūṇ puṭaippap piṟaiyeyiṟ ṟaṉalviḻip pēḻvāy</l>
<l>teḷḷiya ciṅka mākiya tēvait tiruvallik kēṇi<supplied>k</supplied>kaṇ ṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I saw at Tiruvallikkēṇi the deity who became a stout lion with a massive maw,</l>
<l rend="indent">flaming eyes, and curved claws,</l>
<l>When the one without any tolerance for [the fact] that his son,</l>
<l>Who came from school chanting with one-thousand names on his lips,</l>
<l>Was respected as wise, struck a pillar, raging and scorning his child.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
